{"tid":1680923,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動咨詢]4/11 參議院人權與民主法案集氣大會","createTime":"2019-10-29T06:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T14:42:03.000Z","uid":310700,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1980b5988e8361240eeae0408fbe09115c37e8","tid":1680923,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:04:07.000Z","msg":"近日禁多風聲話要pass the act，彭斯演說，GPhone被 DQ，肥佬黎又話Mitch Mcconnell 做緊嘢，但係條act就係上唔到去senate，點解？就係仲差緊條導火線囉！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟想問下大家覺得4/11搞個參議院人權與民主法案集氣大會有冇得諗？？好似上次係House of Representatives 個次勁多議員係嗰邊討論。希望可以再一次複製集會盛景，展現民意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77136aec887e6f3521a528fe80cd84ee8ac121c","tid":1680923,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:05:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"4b8bc6d21116c2aae34a02b39c04631b631e7cf1","tid":1680923,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:05:27.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adec27ae007709caaaf17038c55869c202ba9d9a","tid":16809